{"tid":1721354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:05:31.000Z","uid":4396,"like":205,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"87d9f0d2d70a142a7ec1904e7d52b508ab3fdb41","tid":1721354,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:32.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》】<br />\n<br />\n剛剛習近平在金磚國家領導人會晤上，提出「止暴制亂是香港當前最緊迫的任務」、恐嚇香港人之際，同一時間，美國國會再度出手。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉Mitch McConnell剛剛將《法案》提交參議院審議，並啟動「熱線」（hotline）機制。<br />\n<br />\n在「熱線」機制下，《法案》提交後六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前），沒有參議員反對的話，就當作參議院一致通過，法案就會明早交到白宮處理。<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n🗺【支持眾志國際連結眾籌】<br />\n讓香港人權民主法案遍地開花｜<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc696RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=b923616d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a>"},{"pid":"21dc5a233007a89288cf48676feeea4ccb4f3147","tid":1721354,"uid":4396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1105cdec2421fdd8785bdab035572a2a2c35d20","tid":1721354,"uid":4396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b6ba866efc275db22c1fd0db9e9b411308601f","tid":1721354,"uid":190793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a>